<br>
We'll assume the assassin had a 50% chance to evade to make this simpler (and it's probably reasonably accurate). We want to find out the chance that he evaded at least 14/19 times.<br>
<br>
N=19<br>
r=14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19<br>
<br>
[N!/r!(N-r)!] * 0.5^19 for each r.<br>
<br>
r14=0.0222<br>
r15=0.0074<br>
r16=0.0018<br>
r17+ = insignificant<br>
<br>
So the chance that he would evade at least 14/19 times is 3.15%.<br>
<br>
<br>
Now it's always possible that even though evade is &quot;capped&quot; at 50% that the term is misleading. I know that if a cleric is attacking an infiltrator he evades far more than 50% and it's not capped. Maybe the cap refers to equal weaponskill and defensiveskills....who knows. But lets adjust his evade rate to 55% and see what the chances are he'll evade 14/19 times.<br>
<br>
r14=0.1356<br>
r15=0.0452<br>
r16=0.0113<br>
r17=0.0020<br>
r18+ = insignificant<br>
<br>
You can see that the chance has changed to 19.4% just by raising the evade rate to 55% (he's fully buffed and gets dex/qui raise with lvl so he has higher defensive skill than you have weaponskill).<br>
<br>
<br>
Regardless, 3.15% of occurence isn't that low.<br>
<br>
Yes, I think assassins should be nerfed.   <p>Eka, lvl 50 skald Percival</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=592.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=592.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=592.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=592.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.threadControl?topicID=592.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=592.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=592.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub36.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><t